      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love? I\u2019m parting with this absolute stunner, and let me tell you, it is basically flawless! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as cherished. Come take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
