    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. This example is paired with the preferred Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally superlative with proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings, ensuring the hydraulic steering rack delivers telepathic feedback. The exterior retains its factory luster, while the interior is free of bolster wear or pixel degradation. Mechanically flawless with a comprehensive service history, this is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning purist.",
