    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in breathtaking showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the trim retains its original brilliant shine without a hint of oxidation. Inside, the cabin is equally impressive; the premium leather seats remain supple and firm, showing absolutely no wear, creases, or bolster compression. The dashboard, headliner, and interior accents are immaculate, with every button, switch, and electronic component functioning with factory-new precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and comes with a comprehensive, chronological folder of service records. The engine bay is remarkably clean, and the undercarriage reflects the same level of obsessive care. There are no leaks, no odors, and no compromises. This is, without question, the finest example currently available on the market\u2014a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast who demands the best.",
